Created an attachment (id=55809)
Adds draw and fill Path methods to scaled graphics

Here is a patch for this.  It adds fillPath and drawPath to ScaledGraphics:

/** @see Graphics#drawPath(Path) */
public void drawPath(Path path) {
	graphics.pushState();
	graphics.scale(zoom);
	graphics.drawPath(path);
	graphics.popState();
}

/** @se Graphics#fillPath(Path) */
public void fillPath(Path path) {
	graphics.pushState();
	graphics.scale(zoom);
	graphics.fillPath(path);
	graphics.popState();
}

